                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程所謂的「華語文教材教法」主要是指「非以華語為母語之各種教材的編寫、評鑑與教法」，其課程內容包含以下三大部分： 第一部分：華語文教材教法概論（包含書面教材、多媒體教材、網路教材）  第一週、海內外華語文書面教材的分析與討論第二週、海內外華語文多媒體教材的分析與討論第三週、海內外華語文網路教材的分析與討論第二部分：華語文教材編寫與教案設計(聽說讀寫)第四週、華語文敎學法概說第五週、華語文敎學法之內涵---第一語言與第二語言習得之異同比較第六週、華語文教材編寫與實務第七週、華語文教案設計（一）---「聽與說」部分第八週、華語文教案設計（二）---「讀與寫」部分第九週、華語文教案設計（三）---「讀說讀寫」綜合第十週   期中評量第三部分：華語文教材選用、評鑑與試教第十一週、華語文教材選用與評鑑概說第十二週、自編華語文教材與編寫實務第十三週、試教的理論與實務（華語文敎學觀摩與示範）第十四週、一對一試教與評量（一）第十五週、團體試教與評量（二）---6人（含）以下第十六週、團體試教與評量（二）---6人以上、15人以下第四部分：華語文檢測與評量第十七週、海內外華語文檢測機構與評量方式概說（包含筆試、聽力測驗與面試）第十八週、期末評量上課方式：1.上課宣講---多媒體教學2.敎學觀摩與試教 3.期中作業報告與期末主題報告成績評量方式：１．出席與討論：２０％　 ２．平時作業 ：３０％　 ３．期中報告 ：２５％ ４．期未報告 ：２５％

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                This course “Chinese Language Tutorial Teaching Methods” is to introduce various types of compilation, evaluation and teaching methods of tutorials designed for non-native Chinese speaking students. This course contains the following three parts:I.	Introduction of Chinese language tutorials teaching methods (incl. printed, multimedia, and online tutorials.)Week 1 	Analysis and discussion on printed Chinese language tutorials used in Taiwan and overseasWeek 2 	Analysis and discussion on multimedia Chinese language tutorials used in Taiwan and overseasWeek 3 	Analysis and discussion on online Chinese language tutorials used in Taiwan and overseasII.	Chinese language tutorial compilation & lesson plan design (incl. Listening, Oral, Reading, and Composition)Week 4 	Introduction of Chinese language teaching methodsWeek 5 	Insights of Chinese language teaching methods – Comparisons on native language learning and second language acquisitionWeek 6 	Chinese language tutorials compilation & practice Week 7 	Chinese language lesson plan design I – Listening & OralWeek 8 	Chinese language lesson plan design II – Reading & WritingWeek 9 	Chinese language lesson plan design III – Combination of Listening, Oral, Reading and WritingWeek 10 	Midterm evaluation III. Chinese language tutorials adoption, evaluation, and teaching practiceWeek 11	Introduction of Chinese language tutorials adoption & evaluationWeek 12 	Chinese language tutorials DIY & compilation practice Week 13 	Theory & reality of teaching practice（Chinese language teaching case study & demonstration）Week 14 	One to One teaching practice & evaluation IWeek 15 	Group teaching practice & evaluation I - less than 6 people (incl. 6)Week 16 	Group teaching practice & evaluation II - more than 6, less than 15 peopleIV. Chinese language assessment and evaluationWeek 17 	Introduction of Chinese language assessment institutions & evaluation methods adopted in Taiwan and overseas (incl. paper test, listening test and interview test）Week 18 	Final Report EvaluationInstructional Approaches1. Seminar with multimedia presentation2. Teaching demonstration and practice 3. Midterm report& Final Topic ReportGRADING PLANCoursework will be weighted as follows:1. Attendance & Discussion 	20%　 2. Homework 	30%　 3. Midterm Paper 	25% 4. Final Paper 	25%











