【NEW】2017/07/17


兒童華語文能力測驗（簡稱CCCC）將在8月9日舉行，報名時間從7月17日起至7月26日止，歡迎七至十二歲母語非華語的兒童報考。座位有限, 請儘早報名！ [我要報名] [測驗海報] [CCCC文宣下載] [CCCC能力證書核發規範] [考試題型及註意事項]
                Please be notified that the  formal Children’s Chinese Competency Certification (CCCC）test of 2017 will be administered on August 9. The registration period  is from July 17 to July 26. Welcome the children who are  non-native speakers of Chinese between the ages 7-12 to take the test. The test  seats are limited, seize the chance! [Register  for Test] [Poster] [Download information of CCCC] [Issuance  of CCCC Certificates Regulations] [CCCC sample test item and  test notice] 





【NEW】2017/07/14


6月24日華語文聽力、閱讀預試成績公佈了，考生可先自行登入系統查詢成績，此次考試不寄發成績單與證書，請考生留意！[查詢成績]
The results of the TOCFL Listening & Reading pilot test on June 24 have just come out. Please log in to the website to view your test result(s), pilot test do not serve as official documents and no certificates are issued. [Click Here For My Score] 





【NEW】2017/07/05


國家教育研究院與華測會合作舉辦「華語文語料庫於教學上應用競賽（評量組、教材組）」，歡迎對語料庫應用於華語文教材編輯及評量發展有興趣者參加。
活動日期自即日起至8月16日止，競賽徵稿活動辦法及獎項內容請詳參附件公告。
