※請在報名完成後三天內繳費，以免報名失效。The pilot test of TOCFL Writing (Band C) will be held on April 9, 2016. The registration period is from 9 AM, February 29 to 6 PM, March 18. The processing fee is only NT100 and participants of this test will get a gift on that day. In addition, those who pass Level 5 (C1) will receive gifts worth NT$1,000. Welcome the candidates who are non-native speakers of Chinese to take the test. The test seats are limited, seize the chance! 
