華語文能力測驗將在5月2日及3日舉行，報名時間從3月9日上午9點起至3月27日下午6點止，歡迎母語非華語之人士報考。全省座位/名額有限, 請儘早報名！
                 [我要報名] [測驗海報] [簡章下載] [聽讀能力證書核發規範] 
※同時報考聽力+閱讀、口語、寫作測驗三項者，享有八折優惠！[優惠操作流程]
                Please be notified that the formal TOCFL test of 2015 will be administered on May 2 and 3. The registration period is from 9 AM, March 9 to 6 PM, March 27. Welcome the candidates who are non-native speakers of Chinese to take the test. The test seats are limited, seize the chance!  [Register for Test] [Poster] [Download Regulation] [Issuance of TOCFL Certificates Regulations] 
                ※Take the three tests (Listening & Reading, Speaking and Writing), you can get 20% off your test fee. [Registration Process for Discount]





【NEW】2015/03/04


好消息！為回饋考生，三月預試加碼再抽「10個名額」送市價超過1,500元的超值好禮！機會難得，敬請把握！ 
※請記得參加2015年3月28日的華語文能力測驗預試，若考試當天缺席，就無法獲得超值好禮。[詳細內容] [預試報名] [測驗海報] 
Good News! To appreciate test takers’ support, SC-TOP will prepare the delicate gift (Value NT1,500) for 10 lucky test takers (chosen randomly by the computer) from the pilot test held in March. Please grab this great chance!
P.S. Please ATTEND the mock test on 3/28 to get the gift. In other words, the absent chosen test taker will NOT get the gift. [More Details] [Register for Test]                  [Poster]                    





【NEW】2015/03/04


好消息！為感謝考生支持3月28日舉辦的華語文聽力、閱讀測驗預試，特別於桃園中原大學加開一個考場，請把握機會報名參加！ 
                Good news! In order to respond to the inquiry of test takers, the pilot TOCFL Listening & TOCFL Reading tests held on March 28 will open one more test room in Chung Yuan Christian University in Taoyuan City. Grab the opportunity!





【NEW】2015/02/23


                華語文能力測驗預試將在3月28日舉行，報名時間從2月24日上午9點起至3月6日下午6點止，此次預試各等級僅酌收100元費用，考試當天還可得到小禮物，歡迎母語非華語之人士報考。名額有限，請把握機會報名！
                ※ 預試不提供紙本成績單和證書，考生於測驗結束後可直接於電腦螢幕上看到成績。[詳細內容] [預試報名] [測驗海報] 


The Pilot Test of Test of Chinese as a Foreign Language will be held on March 28. The registration period is from 9 AM, February 24 to 6 PM, March 6. The processing fee is only NT100 for per band and participants of this test will get a gift on that day. Welcome the candidates who are non-native speakers of Chinese to take the test.The test seats are limited, seize the chance! 
                ※Neither the score report nor the certificate will be offered in the pilot test. Test takers’ scores will be shown on the computer screen right after the test.[More Details] [Register for Test]





【NEW】2015/02/20


1月31日華語文聽力、閱讀測驗正式考試（臺灣地區）成績公佈了，考生可先自行登入系統查詢成績，成績單與證書將於2月25日寄出，請考生留意！[查詢成績]


The results of the formal TOCFL Listening & TOCFL Reading test on January 31 (Taiwan) have just come out. Please log in to the website to view your test result(s), and your score reports and certificates will be mailed on February 25. [Click Here For My Score]





【NEW】2015/01/13


自2015年起，華語文聽力、閱讀測驗入門基礎級正式考試將各新增一個題型，聽力測驗新增題型為「對話」，閱讀測驗增設「閱讀理解」題型。[入門基礎級測驗題型變更說明]
                In 2015, TOCFL's Listening and Reading Tests on Band A will each adopt an additional section of test items. There will be a Dialogue section in the Listening Test and a Reading Comprehension section in the Reading Test.[Updates to Test Section Addition in the TOCFL Band A]





【NEW】2015/01/12


華測會將於今年三月舉辦華語文口語測驗評分研習，相關時程及資訊、研習報名錶詳如附件，歡迎更多華語先進參與華測會口語測驗的評分工作！
